               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1360" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1360" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1360" type="surname" value="CODY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1360" type="given" value="JAMES RICHARDSON"></interp>JAMES RICHARDSON CODY</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Philpot-terrace, Edgeware-road. On the 16th of Aug. I was in a field at Paddington, at Father Mathew's teetotal meeting—this parasol was in my boy's hand—he slipped close to a mob, and dropped it, and it was gone in a moment—I do not know who took it—this is it, but it has been altered since I lost it—I know it by the handle—the top has been cut off and made shorter, and the hook has been altered—I took it to pieces myself once, to repair it—I believe it to be mine.</p>
               <p>
